{"tid":1781663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國海外屬地拒絕特區護照持有人入境","createTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T14:30:29.000Z","uid":83713,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b5bf0b2478a4703bf1ef552eae3a1cd227421206","tid":1781663,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"話說小弟有舖旅行癮，成日會check住特區護照幾時多左免簽國<br />\n<br />\n維基網啲資料就好準，仲準過入境處個廢網<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Chinese_citizens_of_Hong_Kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FVisa_requirements_for_Chinese_citizens_of_Hong_Kong&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6vUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=a49e093e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Chinese_citizens_of_Hong_Kong</a><br />\n<br />\n咁大家有冇留意，特區護照holder零零舍舍有個地方比人refuse entry？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKuLrXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKuLrXm.jpg&h=903bfd38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAscension Island，其實邊Q到嚟？原來係St Helena，即係拿破崙比人流放果到既鄰居，大英帝國既海外屬地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dD6h2Am.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdD6h2Am.jpg&h=42f95b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿拿拿，維基都可能錯架，有冇官方醬油先？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ascension-visas.com/faq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ascension-visas.com%2Ffaq&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6vUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=a83dee20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ascension-visas.com/faq</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/quLbnxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FquLbnxD.png&h=eccb6df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據維基，呢個大英海外屬地2015年已經拒絕特區護照持有人入境，但BNO就冇問題<br />\n<br />\n島上面其實得800幾人住，但就有大英同美帝駐軍，仲有海底電纜中轉站<br />\n<br />\n有冇熟IR既巴打知咩事，或者討論下大英咁做，係咪出於咩戰略考慮？留意比佢refuse entry 既，全部都係同支那俄佬關係密切既，或者多恐怖分子既穆斯林國..."},{